# Palate — environment variables
#
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Without a key, Palate runs in demo mode (returns
# mock data) so the UI stays fully functional for screenshots and local work.
#
# NEVER commit .env.local — it is gitignored. Add the key to Vercel's env-var UI for
# production. It stays server-side; no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix means Next.js keeps it out
# of the client bundle.

# Google Gemini API key — free tier at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Uses Gemini 2.0 Flash. Free tier: 1500 requests/day, 15 requests/minute.
GOOGLE_API_KEY=
